$maximumDeposit(MarketState).details: Returns the maximum amount of tokens that can be deposited without reaching the maximum total supply.

$normalizeAmount(MarketState,uint256).details: Normalize an amount of scaled tokens using the current scale factor.

$scaleAmount(MarketState,uint256).details: Scale an amount of normalized tokens using the current scale factor.

$totalSupply(MarketState).details: Returns the normalized total supply of the market.

$liquidityRequired(MarketState).notice: Collateralization requires all pending withdrawals be covered and reserve ratio for remaining liquidity.
